得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"點算帶頭盔呀，咪明確講左第一點係最有可能吹既一點囉，<br />\n你cap依段係講緊未必關縮腳事呀，比較重要既係&quot;obstructing&quot;，<br />\n所以就算個波本身唔經Sigurdsson，佢唔洗縮腳都入波都好，<br />\n佢喺正Ddg面前瞓喺到就有機會越位犯規，睇清楚講咩先喇"},{"pid":"f2f36a90d661e46c6d386c15b7ff5c0c4ffef3c2","tid":1906249,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f7337f43d8f10965d1367d6b2799dfdba390948","tid":1906249,"uid":44285,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb18ee4ef29f02967fb2ca416d23463e30830665","tid":1906249,"uid":72497,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"佢真係獌嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7225e79a18f44b9c3d43d2755f5507023a5b70ac","tid":1906249,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:59:05.000Z","msg":"反曼縮哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji